# Player modifiers
th_heroic_mode_player = {
	all_power_cost = 0.1
	danmaku_power_constant = -0.5
}

	all_power_cost = 0.5
	danmaku_power_constant = -1.0
}

th_lunatic_mode_player = {
	all_power_cost = 0.2
	danmaku_power_constant = -1.5
}
